== 製作 ==
2019年8月上旬，據報導，[[克里斯多福·B·藍登|克里斯多福·B·藍登]]將編劇和執導一部由[[傑森·布倫|傑森·布倫]]的[[布倫屋製片公司|布倫屋製片公司]]製作的恐怖電影，劇情描述一個暴力人物在一個小鎮造成嚴重傷亡。預計將於10月在[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]][[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]開始製作，當時被外界猜測是《[[驚聲尖叫|驚聲尖叫]]》（1996年）的重啟<ref>{{Cite web |last=Fisher |first=Jacob |date=2019-08-05 |title=Christopher Landon Set To Write & Direct New Horror Film For Blumhouse (EXCLUSIVE) |url=https://discussingfilm.net/2019/08/06/christopher-landon-set-to-write-direct-new-horror-film-for-blumhouse-exclusive/ |access-date=2020-09-26 |website=DiscussingFilm |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922040740/https://discussingfilm.net/2019/08/06/christopher-landon-set-to-write-direct-new-horror-film-for-blumhouse-exclusive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。藍登後來澄清重啟《驚聲尖叫》的傳聞，並指出這部電影的靈感是來自{{le|瑪麗·羅傑斯|Mary Rodgers}}的小說《{{le|怪誕星期五|Freaky Friday}}》<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.comicbook.com/horror/news/christopher-landon-blumhouse-happy-death-day-scream/ |title=Happy Death Day Director Offers an Update on His Upcoming Blumhouse Project |website=ComicBook |first=Patrick |last=Cavanaugh |date=2019-08-14 |access-date=2019-10-24 |archive-date=2020-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509132638/https://comicbook.com/horror/news/christopher-landon-blumhouse-happy-death-day-scream/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

8月下旬，官方宣布[[凱瑟琳·紐頓|凱瑟琳·紐頓]]和[[文斯·范恩|文斯·范恩]]簽約擔任主演，其劇本由藍登與麥可·甘迺迪（{{lang|en|Michael Kennedy}}）共同編寫<ref name=":0">{{cite web |url=https://www.deadline.com/2019/08/vince-vaughn-kathryn-newton-chris-landon-body-swapping-blumhouse-thriller-1202707450/ |title=Vince Vaughn, Kathryn Newton Topline Chris Landon Body-Swapping Blumhouse Thriller |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |first=Amanda |last=N'Duka |date=2019-08-29 |access-date=2019-10-24 |archive-date=2019-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115045229/https://deadline.com/2019/08/vince-vaughn-kathryn-newton-chris-landon-body-swapping-blumhouse-thriller-1202707450/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年10月，[[尤賴亞·謝爾頓|尤賴亞·謝爾頓]]、[[亞倫·盧克|亞倫·盧克]]、{{le|凱蒂·芬納蘭|Katie Finneran}}、{{le|賽麗絲·歐康納|Celeste O'Connor}}及米夏·奧西羅維奇（{{lang|en|Misha Osherovich}}）加入演出陣容<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/uriah-shelton-joins-blumhouse-body-swap-movie-1249653 |title='Looking for Alaska' Actor Uriah Shelton Joins Blumhouse Body Swap Movie |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |first=Mia |last=Galuppo |date=2019-10-23 |access-date=2019-10-24 |archive-date=2019-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024035606/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/uriah-shelton-joins-blumhouse-body-swap-movie-1249653 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/succession-alan-ruck-katie-finneran-chris-landon-blumhouse-film-1202768456/ |title='Succession' Star Alan Ruck, Katie Finneran & More Join Chris Landon Blumhouse Film |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |first=Amanda |last=N'Duka |date=2019-10-24 |access-date=2019-10-24 |archive-date=2019-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024224943/https://deadline.com/2019/10/succession-alan-ruck-katie-finneran-chris-landon-blumhouse-film-1202768456/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]於2019年10月21日開始進行<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B34sqVFJ3nu/ |title=Day 1 - AND SO IT BEGINS!! #bodyswap |website=Instagram |date=2019-10-21 |access-date=2019-11-12 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108104828/https://www.instagram.com/p/B34sqVFJ3nu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直至2019年12月12日結束<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B59bhmRpjka/ |title=Day 35 - THE LAST DAY. Gonna miss all these people... 😭 #bodyswap |website=Instagram |date=2019-12-12 |access-date=2019-12-16 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108104829/https://www.instagram.com/p/B59bhmRpjka/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，歷時35天。電影原名為《13號怪誕星期五》（{{lang|en|''Freaky Friday the 13th''}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ajc.com/blog/radiotvtalk/georgia-film-and-production-november-down-from-november-2018/AZ3lvppXwBojyuALwVwACL/ |title=Georgia film and TV production at 36 in November, down from 43 in November 2018 |website=AJC |date=2019-11-12 |access-date=2019-11-12 |archive-date=2019-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112212656/https://www.ajc.com/blog/radiotvtalk/georgia-film-and-production-november-down-from-november-2018/AZ3lvppXwBojyuALwVwACL/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《換人殺砍砍》於2020年10月8日在超越影展（{{lang|en|Beyond Fest}}）上舉行全球首映<ref>{{cite web |url=https://bloody-disgusting.com/indie/3632308/beyond-fest-brings-freaky-archenemy-drive-october/ |title=Beyond Fest Brings ''Freaky'', ''Archenemy'', ''Possessor'', ''Saint Maud'' and More to the Drive-In This October |work={{le|Bloody Disgusting|Bloody Disgusting}} |access-date=2020-09-19 |archive-date=2020-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003020522/https://bloody-disgusting.com/indie/3632308/beyond-fest-brings-freaky-archenemy-drive-october/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[環球影業|環球影業]]將該片定於2020年11月13日在美國院線上映<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/freaky-vince-vaughn-universal-blumhouse-fall-release-1234574292/ |title=Universal Sets Blumhouse Body-Swap Movie ''Freaky'' For Fall Theatrical Release |website=Deadline Hollywood |first=Anthony |last=D'Alessandro |date=2020-09-10 |access-date=2020-09-10 |archive-date=2020-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910165238/https://deadline.com/2020/09/freaky-vince-vaughn-universal-blumhouse-fall-release-1234574292/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後於2020年12月4日安排在[[隨選視訊|VOD]]上發行<ref name="Bruggerman-Oct2020">{{cite web |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/10/universal-theaters-short-windows-the-croods-and-freaky-1234590295/ |title=As Bond Vacates 2020, Universal Offers Theaters Short Windows on ''The Croods'' and ''Freaky'' |website=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]] |first=Tom |last=Bruggerman |date=2020-10-02 |access-date=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201005203148/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/10/universal-theaters-short-windows-the-croods-and-freaky-1234590295/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

